item.title: Yeha this problem
item.dc:creator: @waffle1 waffle`
item.description:
@waffle1 wrote:

Alot of the times when you get multiple errors like this it is because you left a bracket open that needs to be closed. Look at where you were adding the title box, try adding a } at the end or removing one. If this doesn’t work post the code for the box on here and I’ll see if I can spot a problem with the code.

No guarantees.

EDIT: After looking at the errors it says that a “;” is expected, you somewhere in there deleted a symbol you shouldn’t have. Sometimes when it says “;” you still deleted “}” it’s just saying that you need a “;” because its trying to find a way to fix it.
